OL,7,FA report by the think tank calls on Ms
OL,8,FReeves to undertake serious tax
OL,9,Freform, instead of reaching for an
OL,10,F"eclectic grab bag of tax raisers",
OL,11,Fwhich could further complicate the
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,FIt comes after the Resolution
OL,15,FFoundation proposed a 2p cut in
OL,16,Fnational insurance, matched by a 2p
OL,17,Frise in income tax, to create a "level
OL,18,Fplaying field" and protect workers'
OL,19,Fpay.
